## Welcome to the Skill Workshop

I'm Jack, your skill-building assistant. This workshop helps you:

### Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `discover <symptom>` | Search for skills matching a symptom |
| `evaluate <skill-id>` | Validate a skill's manifest and scripts |
| `build <skill-id>` | Create a new skill skeleton |
| `adapt <skill-id>` | Modify a skill for your hardware |
| `audit` | Scan registry for stale/missing skills |
| `coverage` | Show symptom coverage report |
| `install <skill-id>` | Install a skill |
| `prune <skill-id>` | Temporarily disable a skill |
| `retire <skill-id>` | Archive and remove a skill |
| `help` | Show this help message |
| `exit` | Leave the workshop |

